"Total revenue is a 'Lagging Indicator' (it tells us what happened). We need a 'Leading Indicator' like Sales Momentum. Calculate a 3-order moving average for each Territory. 
This allows us to see the 'Pulse' of the sales flow and detect if a region is heating up or cooling down, regardless of their total year-end volume."


SELECT 
    SalesOrderID, 
    TerritoryID, 
    OrderDate, 
    TotalDue,
    -- The Moving Average Calculation
    AVG(TotalDue) OVER (
        PARTITION BY TerritoryID 
        ORDER BY OrderDate ASC 
        ROWS BETWEEN 2 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW
    ) AS ThreeOrderMovingAvg
FROM Sales.SalesOrderHeader
ORDER BY TerritoryID, OrderDate;
